title: Ella Fitzgerald - Jazz 'Round Midnight
description:
[quote]By Kindle Customer

Of all the Ella CD's I have, this is the one I keep in my CD player...When I listen to her incredible fluidity on the song "'Round Midnight," I am, despite the theme of the song, instantly transported into bliss because her angelic voice makes me so glad that such a recording(among many others of hers) exists for us to listen to.. over, and over again. Ella is my therapist, and no matter how bad a day I might have had, she is my stress-buster. Works every time.There is no denying that she cannot be categorized..she is on another level completely in the world of music. Buy this CD..you will cherish it.[/quote]
